nodes.text: A rebel cell existed at some point during the outbreak of the Galactic Civil War. Following the Battle of Hoth in 3 ABY, the Rebel Alliance cell was attacked by the 204th Imperial Fighter Wing, which obliterated the cell's contingent of X-wing starfighters while the Pursuer destroyed the cell's EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate.
